summary:
I am extremely motivated to try myself out in various fields; develop my skills and push my limits. Working with people and share common knowledge, motivation, inspiration and energy are one of my biggest desires. As well as, I find that creating a working environment that feels like my second home on an objective and spiritual level is equally crucial.
Skilled in Python and MATLAB (Programming language and platform), Microsoft Office Suite, Statistical Modeling, STATA (software for data science), Team Building, Management, and Leadership. Strong operations professional with a Bachelor's degree focused in Economics and Business Economics from Vrije Universiteit Amsterdam.
